    "• BERT4Rec [37].",
    "A bidirectional self-attention-based sequential recommender.",
    "It uses the Transformer encoder to predict randomly masked items in a sequence by conditioning on both their left and right context, thereby capturing user historical behaviors.",
    "An encoder-decoder Transformer-based approach that unifies different recommendation related tasks into a single generative LLM.",
    "For our sequential recommendation downstream task, we adopt the personalized prompts from OpenP5 [51] and apply the same random indexing method to items as used in our ToolRec."
